---
// Dismissible disclaimer banner — reappears each visit (no persistent storage)
---

<div
  id="disclaimer-banner"
  class="relative bg-accent/90 text-white text-center text-sm py-2 px-4 z-50"
>
  <p class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    ⚠️ 本網站為獨立社群專案，與 OpenClaw 官方無任何關聯。內容僅供參考。
    <a href="/about" class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-light ml-1">
      了解更多
    </a>
  </p>
  <button
    id="dismiss-disclaimer"
    class="absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-white/80 hover:text-white text-lg leading-none cursor-pointer"
    aria-label="關閉免責聲明"
  >
    ✕
  </button>
</div>

<script>
  document.getElementById('dismiss-disclaimer')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    document.getElementById('disclaimer-banner')?.remove();
  });
</script>
